Mr President , as draftsman for the Committee on Citizens &apos; Freedoms and Rights , Justice and Home Affairs , I have no problem asking this House to vote in favour of the amendments tabled by the Committee on Budgets on the initiative of either our committee or the general rapporteur , Mrs Haug .
